  "title": "IT Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>KHA Pte Ltd is an architectural and interior design services company.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will ensure the seamless operation of office IT infrastructure to support business functions, managing communication systems, security, and data organization to enhance productivity and operational efficiency.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain and troubleshoot office IT software and hardware to ensure uninterrupted daily business operations</li><li>Manage and optimize emailing systems and in-house communication platforms to facilitate effective internal and external communication</li><li>Oversee online meeting technologies, including equipment and software, to support virtual collaboration and business continuity</li><li>Implement and monitor IT security measures to protect company data and systems from threats</li><li>Organize and manage data storage and distribution processes to ensure efficient access and compliance with business needs</li><li>Optimize software license usage and computer system configurations to maximize resource efficiency and cost-effectiveness</li><li>Apply graphic design skills and/or maintain the company website to support marketing and communication efforts (optional)</li></ul>",
